IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
User italoamaya
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -s mu4e-icloud -a italoamaya -w"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
AuthMechs PLAIN
SystemCertificates no
CertificateFile ~/.maildir/certificates/root-certificates.pem

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.maildir/icloud/
Inbox ~/.maildir/icloud/INBOX

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

